<%= email_image_tag("Opus_Icon.png") %>
<h2>Dear <%= @user.username %>,</h2>
<p>
  You have requested for a password reset, please click on the following link to do so.
</p>
<p>
  <%= ENV.fetch("HOST") { "http://localhost:3000" } %>/reset?token=<%= @user.reset_password_token %> <br />
  The link's validity lasts for 4 hours. 
</p>
<p>Thanks for using Opus!</p>